						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the Hanumān temple.</p>						

						<p>Sadāśivarāya, 1553 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1475, Pramādīcha, Āśvija ba. 3, Saturday, corresponding to 1553 A.D., September 23, Saturday f.d.t. °87.</p>						

						<p>It records the remission of taxes on the barbers of Mudugal-sīme at the request of Timmōja, Koṇḍōja and Bhadrōja.</p>						

						</summary>
